RECONSIDERATION DOCKET

96-84. Goldberg Cos., Inc. v. Richmond Hts. Council.

Cuyahoga App. Nos. 68291 and 68292. Reported at 79 Ohio St.3d 1205, 679 N.E.2d 716. On motion for reconsideration. Motion granted; the merits will be decided on the merit briefs that have already been filed.

Moyer, C.J., and Lundberg Stratton, J., dissent.
